### Left Icon Rail Widget

#### [NEW] [library_icon_rail.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/dashboard/presentation/widgets/library_icon_rail.dart)

A new widget for the always-visible left icon rail.

**Visual spec:**
- Width: **32px**
- Background: `Colors.grey[900]`
- Contains two icon buttons stacked vertically at the top:
  - `Icons.library_music` (size 18) — Songs
  - `Icons.menu_book` (size 18) — Bible
- Icon color: `Colors.white38` (inactive), `Colors.white` (active/hovered)
- Active indicator: 2px left border accent in `Colors.deepPurpleAccent` on the active icon (only when pane is visible)
- Each icon wrapped in `Tooltip` with labels "Songs (Q)" and "Bible (S)"
- Vertical padding between icons: **4px**

**Tap logic** (implemented in the widget):
```
onTap(tappedIndex):
  if pane is visible AND tappedIndex == current active tab:
    hide pane (in pinned mode only — toggle off)
  else if pane is visible AND tappedIndex != current active tab:
    switch to tapped tab
  else (pane is hidden):
    show pane on tapped tab
```

