### Main Dashboard Layout — Restructured

#### [MODIFY] [main_dashboard_page.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/dashboard/presentation/pages/main_dashboard_page.dart)

The main layout row changes from:

```
[ LibraryPane (flex:8) ] | [ Setlist (flex:3) ] | [ Slides+Monitors (flex:9) ]
```

To:

```
[ IconRail (32px fixed) ] [ LibraryPane (flex:8, conditional) ] | [ Setlist (flex:3) ] | [ Slides+Monitors (flex:9) ]
```

**When pinned + visible:**
```
[ Rail 32px ][ Library flex:8 ]|[ Setlist flex:3 ]|[ Slides+Monitors flex:9 ]
```
Layout is docked. Library pane takes space normally.

**When pinned + hidden** (user toggled via rail icon):
```
[ Rail 32px ]|[ Setlist flex:3 ]|[ Slides+Monitors flex:9 ]
```
Library pane removed from layout. Remaining panes expand.

**When auto-hide + hidden:**
```
[ Rail 32px ]|[ Setlist flex:3 ]|[ Slides+Monitors flex:9 ]
```
Same as above — Library pane not in layout.

**When auto-hide + visible** (user clicked rail icon to temporarily open):
```
[ Rail 32px ][ OVERLAY: Library pane ]
             [ Setlist flex:3 ]|[ Slides+Monitors flex:9 ]
```
Library pane renders as an **overlay** (via `Stack` + `Positioned`) on top of the content. A semi-transparent barrier behind it detects clicks to dismiss. The overlay has:
- Same width as the docked version would have (~40% of remaining width, or a fixed pixel width like 320px — whichever looks better)
- Drop shadow on the right edge: `BoxShadow(color: Colors.black54, blurRadius: 8, offset: Offset(2, 0))`
- Full height (below title bar, above bottom)

**Implementation approach:**
- Wrap the main `Row` in a `Stack`
- The `Row` always contains the `IconRail` + remaining panes
- When pinned + visible, the `LibraryPane` is inside the `Row` (docked, takes flex space)
- When auto-hide + visible, the `LibraryPane` is in a `Positioned` overlay in the `Stack`
- A `GestureDetector` barrier behind the overlay catches taps to dismiss

**Song Editor mode**: When `isEditorOpen` is true, the existing behavior is preserved. The icon rail remains visible. If Library pane is hidden, the editor still takes its full flex:12 space.

